Class Player

  • java.lang.Object
    • nz.ac.vuw.ecs.swen225.a3.maze.Player

  • public class Player
extends java.lang.Object
    The player of the game, represented as Chap. Holds an inventory of items that have been picked up, and a count of treasures that have been collected.
